    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented here is a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish paired with an interior preserved in a showroom-fresh state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this offering represents the definitive benchmark for its class.",
