      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, maintains its original showroom luster. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the connoisseur who demands nothing less than absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
